<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 14:07:08 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>因意大利政府反对而被撤销西岸市长大使职务</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/west-bank-mayors-ambassadorship-revoked-following-italian-govt-opposition/0000018e-18d6-d8fb-abff-5dde377e0000</link><description>意大利政府对任命本尼·卡什里尔（Benny Kasriel）担任以色列驻该国特使表示担忧，因为他住在约旦河西岸。谈判未果，外交部发布了该职位的内部招标</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 13:11:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/west-bank-mayors-ambassadorship-revoked-following-italian-govt-opposition/0000018e-18d6-d8fb-abff-5dde377e0000</guid></item><item><title>国家检察官阻止对父亲被指控强奸未成年人的以色列 MK 进行审讯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/state-prosecutor-prevents-interrogation-of-mk-whose-father-is-accused-of-raping-minors/0000018e-184b-d8fb-abff-5d4b7f170000</link><description>MK Yaakov Tessler 涉嫌向一名 15 岁受害者支付封口费，该受害者据称被 Tessler 的父亲强奸。尽管案件已搁置六个月，但他的调查尚未获得国家检察官的授权</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 11:19:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/state-prosecutor-prevents-interrogation-of-mk-whose-father-is-accused-of-raping-minors/0000018e-184b-d8fb-abff-5d4b7f170000</guid></item><item><title>由于战争，以色列部长取消了一年一度的独立日烟花表演</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-nixes-annual-independence-day-fireworks-show-due-to-war/0000018e-188a-d1cc-abfe-dfafc31e0000</link><description>利库德集团部长米里·雷格夫对鉴于严峻的形势，第76届独立日仪式未能按照传统举行表示遗憾。两年前，烟花表演也因患有创伤后应激障碍 (PTSD) 的退伍军人的反对而被取消</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 11:12:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-nixes-annual-independence-day-fireworks-show-due-to-war/0000018e-188a-d1cc-abfe-dfafc31e0000</guid></item><item><title>自战争开始以来，已有 27 名加沙被拘留者在以色列军事设施的拘留期间死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/27-gaza-detainees-died-in-custody-at-israeli-army-facilities-since-the-start-of-the-war/0000018e-1322-d950-a18e-f3bbaa370000</link><description>返回加沙的被拘留者作证称，他们受到了严酷的待遇，包括士兵和审讯期间的殴打和虐待。以色列国防军发言人表示，军方已对死亡事件展开调查</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 10:57:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/27-gaza-detainees-died-in-custody-at-israeli-army-facilities-since-the-start-of-the-war/0000018e-1322-d950-a18e-f3bbaa370000</guid></item><item><title>以色列奖司法小组要求加入高等法院，反对教育部长取消大多数奖项的决定</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-prize-panel-asks-to-join-petitions-against-ministers-decision-to-nix-most-awards/0000018e-180d-d1cc-abfe-dfadb2a20000</link><description>司法小组表示，应该允许它成为请愿书的一方，“因为它拥有大量事实信息，如果没有这些信息，在保密的幌子下，不得将其提交高等法院”</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 10:41:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-prize-panel-asks-to-join-petitions-against-ministers-decision-to-nix-most-awards/0000018e-180d-d1cc-abfe-dfadb2a20000</guid></item><item><title>当人类离开时，乌鸦会玩耍吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-03-07/ty-article-magazine/do-crows-play-when-the-humans-are-away/0000018e-1821-d8fb-abff-5d2be6010000</link><description>以色列在新冠病毒大流行期间进行的一项研究分析了人类（据称）被限制在家里时三种鸟类的行为，结果表明生活在我们中间的野生动物适应得非常快</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 09:49:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-03-07/ty-article-magazine/do-crows-play-when-the-humans-are-away/0000018e-1821-d8fb-abff-5d2be6010000</guid></item><item><title>在内塔尼亚胡的统治下，以色列还会遭受多少死亡和灾难？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/how-many-more-deaths-and-disasters-will-israel-endure-under-netanyahus-watch/0000018e-1538-d792-a7be-3db8cd320000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡总理助长了宗教与国家之间的腐败关系，导致梅龙灾难的发生。他对调查委员会报告的回应反映了报告中描述的腐败文化</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 04:00:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/how-many-more-deaths-and-disasters-will-israel-endure-under-netanyahus-watch/0000018e-1538-d792-a7be-3db8cd320000</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩正在等待加沙停火以结束与以色列的争端</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/lebanon-is-waiting-for-a-ceasefire-in-gaza-to-end-its-dispute-with-israel/0000018e-15ed-d8fb-abff-55eff96b0000</link><description>美国越来越多地参与以色列北部边境的敌对行动以及这场冲突与加沙战争之间的联系。为了取得成功，华盛顿特使需要内塔尼亚胡和纳斯鲁拉合作</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 04:00:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/lebanon-is-waiting-for-a-ceasefire-in-gaza-to-end-its-dispute-with-israel/0000018e-15ed-d8fb-abff-55eff96b0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯代表团离开开罗，停火谈判下周续签</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article-live/idf-soldier-killed-13-wounded-in-gaza-fighting-hamas-says-talks-on-verge-of-collapse/0000018e-16ed-d792-a7be-3efd76930000</link><description>以色列外交部称“南非继续充当哈马斯的合法机构” ■ 哈马斯代表团在没有人质协议的情况下离开开罗，谈判将于下周恢复 ■ 挪威建议公司不要与约旦河西岸定居点开展任何业务 ■ 报告：如果以色列国防军入侵拉法，美国考虑限制以色列使用美国武器</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 03:42:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article-live/idf-soldier-killed-13-wounded-in-gaza-fighting-hamas-says-talks-on-verge-of-collapse/0000018e-16ed-d792-a7be-3efd76930000</guid></item><item><title>塔夫茨大学的犹太学生在抵制以色列的辩论中吐口水、受到侮辱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/jewish-students-spat-on-insulted-during-debate-on-boycotting-israel-at-tufts-university/0000018e-15af-d7d3-abce-75af548d0000</link><description>几名参与者向大学警察提出骚扰投诉，校长苏尼尔·库马尔表示调查已经启动</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 22:09:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/jewish-students-spat-on-insulted-during-debate-on-boycotting-israel-at-tufts-university/0000018e-15af-d7d3-abce-75af548d0000</guid></item><item><title>Khubeza，加沙巴勒斯坦人在饥饿和战争加剧的情况下寻找的野生植物</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/khubeza-the-wild-plant-palestinians-in-gaza-are-foraging-for-amid-soaring-hunger-and-war/0000018e-13b5-d32b-ab8f-bbfd437f0000</link><description>锦葵在交通岛、路边和田野中自由生长，一直是巴勒斯坦的季节性食物。现在，在饱受战争蹂躏的加沙地带缺乏有组织的援助的情况下，它正在为加沙人提供重要的营养和生计</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 21:34:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/khubeza-the-wild-plant-palestinians-in-gaza-are-foraging-for-amid-soaring-hunger-and-war/0000018e-13b5-d32b-ab8f-bbfd437f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列东耶路撒冷发展管理局所有员工被解雇；实施面临危险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/all-employees-of-east-jerusalem-development-admin-fired-implementation-in-jeopardy/0000018e-1570-d8fb-abff-557a3c9a0000</link><description>东耶路撒冷发展管理局负责制定和管理五年计划，并充当居民和当局之间的中间人。一位消息人士称，七名员工被解雇后，“感觉一切都崩溃了”</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 21:16:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/all-employees-of-east-jerusalem-development-admin-fired-implementation-in-jeopardy/0000018e-1570-d8fb-abff-557a3c9a0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日，哈马斯性暴力事件引发疯狂的否认主义狂潮</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/the-unhinged-denialist-frenzy-around-hamas-sexual-violence-on-october-7/0000018e-14d0-d2aa-a1be-1dd5f91a0000</link><description>媒体和专家对 10 月 7 日哈马斯性暴力事件进行阴谋性否认，这让他们自己和美国左派蒙羞。但延长加沙战争的呼吁可能会延续针对人质的恐怖行为</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 21:02:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/the-unhinged-denialist-frenzy-around-hamas-sexual-violence-on-october-7/0000018e-14d0-d2aa-a1be-1dd5f91a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙地带南部战斗中丧生； 13人受伤，其中5人伤势严重</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-killed-in-south-gaza-strip-fighting-13-wounded-five-seriously/0000018e-157b-d7d3-abce-75fb06720000</link><description>该士兵是参谋军士。 David Sasson，21 岁，来自 Ganot Hadar</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 20:49:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-killed-in-south-gaza-strip-fighting-13-wounded-five-seriously/0000018e-157b-d7d3-abce-75fb06720000</guid></item><item><title>一场又一场惨败：梅龙灾难报告还认定内塔尼亚胡对 10 月 7 日有罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/one-big-fiasco-mount-meron-disaster-report-also-convicts-netanyahu-for-october-7/0000018e-1508-d2aa-a1be-1dcd1d410000</link><description>该委员会成员对内塔尼亚胡“你不能对你不知道的事情负责”的论点印象不深。一旦预先警告多年的10月7日大屠杀接受调查，他将无法依靠这个辩护</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 19:08:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/one-big-fiasco-mount-meron-disaster-report-also-convicts-netanyahu-for-october-7/0000018e-1508-d2aa-a1be-1dcd1d410000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府：也为暴力侵害妇女的权利而战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-06/ty-article/.highlight/israels-government-is-fighting-for-the-right-to-be-violent-at-home-too/0000018e-14b0-d8fb-abff-55ba1f630000</link><description>以色列国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本-格维尔（Itamar Ben-Gvir）和他的极右翼政党 Otzma Yehudit 一直在努力剥离女性人口，以减缓进展</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 18:27:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-06/ty-article/.highlight/israels-government-is-fighting-for-the-right-to-be-violent-at-home-too/0000018e-14b0-d8fb-abff-55ba1f630000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 152 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-152/0000018e-14f6-d1cc-abfe-d7ff963c0000</link><description>哈马斯消息人士称，与以色列的谈判正处于崩溃的边缘。 白宫称，如果哈马斯同意释放所有病人、老人和妇女人质，则可能停火六周。 也门胡塞武装疑似袭击了海湾的一艘商船美国官员表示，亚丁风暴造成“人员伤亡” ■ 战争开始 152 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 18:19:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-152/0000018e-14f6-d1cc-abfe-d7ff963c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列下周允许阿联酋资助的人道主义援助通过海上进入加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/israel-to-allow-entry-via-sea-of-uae-funded-humanitarian-aid-into-gaza-next-week/0000018e-1490-d1cc-abfe-d7bd0ca20000</link><description>当地卫生官员称，海上航线的开通预计将导致国际社会对以色列在加沙的人道主义危机提出更多批评，由于以色列在援助物资转移方面设置困难，迄今为止已有 18 人死亡。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 16:56:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/israel-to-allow-entry-via-sea-of-uae-funded-humanitarian-aid-into-gaza-next-week/0000018e-1490-d1cc-abfe-d7bd0ca20000</guid></item><item><title>尤瓦尔·亚伯拉罕是一位真正的英雄，因为他没有在种族隔离的重压下呻吟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-06/ty-article-opinion/.premium/yuval-abraham-is-actually-a-true-hero-for-not-groaning-under-the-weight-of-apartheid/0000018e-1433-d73e-af9f-7fb7d85a0000</link><description>以色列电影制片人在柏林电影节上的获奖感言似乎冒犯了《国土报》记者的敏感耳朵</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 16:34:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-06/ty-article-opinion/.premium/yuval-abraham-is-actually-a-true-hero-for-not-groaning-under-the-weight-of-apartheid/0000018e-1433-d73e-af9f-7fb7d85a0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡和甘茨勉强的政治婚姻显示出稳定的曙光</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-and-gantzs-reluctant-political-marriage-shows-glimpses-of-stability/0000018e-1283-d547-a19e-92935e450000</link><description>本尼·甘茨的美国之行可能羞辱了内塔尼亚胡，但并没有真正威胁到以色列的战时政府 ■ 总理决定允许斋月期间在阿克萨清真寺进行礼拜自由，这表明了政府极右翼势力的局限性</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 16:27:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-and-gantzs-reluctant-political-marriage-shows-glimpses-of-stability/0000018e-1283-d547-a19e-92935e450000</guid></item></channel></rss>